(545, 'Re: Katy flatlands280824', 'Re: Katy flatlands', 'phillip.allen@enron.com', 'al.pollard@enron.com', 'Al,\n\nI am not in good enough shape to ride a century right now.  Plus I\'m nursing \nsome injuries.  I can do lunch this week or next, let\'s pick a day.\n\nPhillip', '[\"good\", \"shape\", \"ride\", \"century\", \"right\", \"plus\", \"nursing\", \"injury\", \"lunch\", \"week\"]', NULL, 'Informational'),
