(627, 'RE: a/c for #27567476', 'RE: a/c for #27', 'phillip.allen@enron.com', 'maryrichards7@hotmail.com', 'Go ahead and order the ac for #27.  \nCan you email or fax a summary of all rents collected from August through \nDecember.  I need this to finish my tax return.\nI have all the expense data but not rent collection.  Fax number is \n713-646-3239.\n\nThank you,\n\nPhillip', '[\"rent\", \"ahead\", \"order\", \"email\", \"summary\", \"collected\", \"august\", \"december\", \"finish\", \"tax\"]', NULL, 'Informational'),
